  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Blessed with the genetics of the ancient Sage Bat, your physiology is inherently molded for greatness. At 3rd level, you gain the following traits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Movement speed increases by 5ft, and you gain a wall walking speed equal to your movement speed.</p></li><li><p>You have advantage on Strength Checks to Push, Pull and Drag objects.</p></li><li><p>As a reaction to making a Strength or Dexterity saving throw, you may spend 3 chakra to make at advantage. At 11th level, you may spend 7 chakra to do this without spending a reaction, up to once per round.</p></li></ul>",
